node.text:
💚🐢 Taricaya turtle release!
These turtles have suffered greatly due to lack of human conscience, the effects of gold mining and the contamination of their habitat. Now these little ones have a new opportunity thanks to the Taricaya Turtle Repopulation Project!

Credits: @mikaelaswildlife & @taricaya.eco.reserve.

Mikaela said: “Every night we go out searching for their eggs on the beach before they can be taken for food, incubate them at camp and then release them back into the wild where they belong!”
